Package com.example.cardiocare

Class UserMeasurementDetails

java.lang.Object
com.example.cardiocare.UserMeasurementDetails
public class UserMeasurementDetails extends Object
Class representing user measurement details. Contains information about a specific measurement, such as date, time, systolic value, diastolic value, heart rate, comment, and key.
